      "title": "Provincial schools in the south are open five days a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Southern Provincial Education Department says that all schools governed by the Southern Provincial Council will be open five days a week from tomorrow (25).",
        "Schools under the Ministry of Education have decided to hold only a few days a week."
      ],
